            You coyly ask permission to voice the heresy that
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">formalism</ENAMEX> is overrated, as if we are writing in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1970</TIMEX> and you have something
brave to say. Come on, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Deborah</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Formalism</ENAMEX> has been the theory non grata
